---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---


<MainLayout title="Home">
	<section class="hero">
		<article class="hero__article">
			<img src="/dinosaurio-hero.png" alt="" class="hero__img">
			<div class="hero__text">
				<h1 class="hero__title">Sumérgete en el increíble mundo de los <span>Dinosaurios</span>!</h1>
				<p class="hero__desc">Descubre la historia y la diversidad de los dinosaurios en esta emocionante aventura de exploración.</p>
			</div>
		</article>
	</section>
	<section class="about">
		<article class="about__article">
			<p class="about__subtitle">Pero primero que nada...</p>
			<h2 class="about__title">¿Qué son los Dinosaurios?</h2>
			<div class="about__flex">
				<div class="about__img__cont">
					<img src="/9693731.jpg" alt="" class="about__img">
				</div>
				<div class="about__text">
					<p class="about__desc">Los dinosaurios fueron un grupo diverso de reptiles prehistóricos que dominaron la Tierra durante más de <span>160 millones de años</span>, desde el <span>periodo Triásico</span> (hace unos 250 millones de años) hasta el final del <span>Cretácico</span> (hace 66 millones de años).</p>
					<p class="about__desc">Eran animales terrestres en su mayoría, pero existieron también especies voladoras y acuáticas. Aunque muchos se extinguieron, <span>las aves actuales son descendientes directos de los dinosaurios</span>.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</article>
		<article class="features__article">
			<h2 class="features__title">Características principales</h2>
			<ul class="features__list">
				<li class="features__item">
					<img src="/tamaños.png" alt="" class="features__img">
					<span>Diversidad de tamaños:</span> desde menos de 1 metro hasta más de 30 metros de largo</li>
				<li class="features__item">
					<img src="/alimentacion.png" alt="" class="features__img">
					<span>Tipos de alimentación:</span> herbívoros, carnívoros, omnívoros.
				</li>
				<li class="features__item">
					<img src="/erguido.png" alt="" class="features__img">
					<span>Postura erguida:</span> a diferencia de otros reptiles, sus patas estaban colocadas debajo del cuerpo, permitiéndoles mejor movilidad.
				</li>
				<li class="features__item">
					<img src="/veloz.png" alt="" class="features__img">
					<span>Velocidad:</span> muchos de los dinosaurios eran veloces, con velocidades de hasta 80 km/h.
				</li>
			</ul>
		</article>
		<div class="about__footer">
			<p class="about__ending">Los dinosaurios no fueron solo monstruos gigantes; <span>fueron parte crucial de la evolución y de la historia de la vida en la Tierra</span>.</p>
			<a href="/dinosaurios" class="about__btn">Ver las distintas especies</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</MainLayout>

<style>

	/* Hero Section Styles */

	.hero {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		min-height: 100svh;
		background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)),url("../../public/hero.webp") no-repeat center center/cover;
		padding-top: 110.25px;
		z-index: 1;
		padding-bottom: 5rem;
		.hero__article {
			max-width: 90%;
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
			.hero__img {
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 18rem;
				height: auto;
				border-radius: 1rem;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
				opacity: 0;
				animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out forwards; 
			}
			.hero__title {
				font-size: 2.6rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				color: var(--white);
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				line-height: 1.3;
				text-wrap: pretty;
				margin-bottom: .5rem;
				opacity: 0;
				animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out .2s forwards;
				font-weight: 500;
				max-width: 40ch;
				span {
					color: var(--primary-color);
					letter-spacing: 2px;
					text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--primary-color-glow);
				}
			}
			.hero__desc {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				color: var(--light-grey);
				text-align: center;
				margin: 0 auto;
				opacity: 0;
				animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out .4s forwards;
				max-width: 40ch;
			}
			.hero__btn {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
				background-color: var(--primary-color);
				color: var(--white);
				text-decoration: none;
				border-radius: 0.5rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
			}
		}
	}

	/* Media Queries */

	@media (width > 480px) {
		.hero {
			.hero__article {
				.hero__img {
					max-width: 25rem;
				}
				.hero__title {
					font-size: 3rem;
				}
			}
		}
	}
	@media (width > 768px) {
		.hero {
			.hero__article {
				flex-direction: row;
				column-gap: 3rem;
				justify-content: center;
				.hero__img {
					max-width: 28rem;
				}
				.hero__text {
					width: 50%;
				}
				.hero__desc {
					text-align: left;
					max-width: unset;
				}
				.hero__title {
					text-align: left;
					
				}
			}
			
		}
	}

	/* About Section Styles */

	.about {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: url("/lluvia-asteroides.png") no-repeat top right,linear-gradient(var(--black), var(--black));
		background-size: 0rem, cover;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		.about__article {
			max-width: 90%;
			margin: 0 auto;
			.about__flex {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				background-color: var(--light-black);
				border-radius: 1rem;
			}
			.about__text {
				padding: 1rem;
			}
			.about__subtitle {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				color: var(--light-grey);
				font-weight: 600;
				text-align: center;
			}
			.about__title {
				font-size: 2.4rem;
				color: var(--white);
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
				font-weight: 500;
				text-align: center;
				&:after {
					content: '';
					display: block;
					width: 100px;
					height: 4px;
					background-color: var(--primary-color);
					margin: 0.5rem auto;
					border-radius: 2px;
				}

			}
			.about__img__cont {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
				align-items: center;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 550px;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
				max-height: 400px;
				overflow: hidden;
				border-radius: 1rem 1rem 0 0;
			}
			.about__img {
				border-radius: 1rem 1rem 0 0;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				object-fit: cover;
			}
			.about__desc {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				color: var(--light-grey);
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
				line-height: 1.8;
				max-width: 55ch;
				text-align: left;
				span {
					color: var(--white);
					font-weight: 600;
				}
			}
			.about__btn {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
				background-color: var(--primary-hover);
				color: var(--white);
				text-decoration: none;
				border-radius: 0.5rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
			}
		}
		.features__article {
			max-width: 90%;
			margin: 2rem auto;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
			text-align: center;
			.features__title {
				font-size: 2.4rem;
				color: var(--white);
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
				font-weight: 500;
				&:after {
					content: '';
					display: block;
					width: 100px;
					height: 4px;
					background-color: var(--secondary-color);
					margin: 0.5rem auto;
					border-radius: 2px;
				}
			}
			.features__list {
				list-style-type: none;
				padding: 0;
				margin: 0 auto;
				max-width: 40ch;
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				gap: 1rem;
				justify-items: center;
				.features__item {
					font-size: 1.1rem;
					color: var(--light-grey);
					margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
					text-align: left;
					line-height: 1.6;
					background-color: var(--secondary-color);
					padding: 1.5rem;
					border-radius: 0.5rem;
					max-width: 330px;
					span {
						color: var(--white);
						font-weight: 600;
					}
				}
				.features__img {
					
				}
			}
		}
		.about__footer {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			width: 90%;
			margin: 0 auto;
			margin-top: 1rem;
		}
		.about__ending {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
			color: var(--light-grey);
			max-width: 50ch;
			line-height: 1.6;
			span {
				color: var(--white);
				font-weight: 600;
			}
		}
		.about__btn {
			display: inline-block;
			padding: 1rem;
			background-color: var(--secondary-color);
			color: var(--white);
			text-decoration: none;
			border-radius: 0.5rem;
			font-weight: 600;
			margin-top: 1.5rem;
			width: 100%;
			max-width: 25rem;
			text-align: center;
		}
	}

	/* About Section Media Queries */

	@media (width > 480px) {
		.about {
			.about__article {
				.about__title {
					font-size: 3rem;
				}
				.about__text {
					padding: 2rem;
				}
				.about__img__cont {
					align-self: stretch;
					max-width: 100%;
				}
			}
			.features__article {
				.features__title {
					font-size: 3rem;
				}
				.features__list {
					max-width: 60ch;
					grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
					.features__img {
						display: block;
					}
					.features__item {
						max-width: unset;
					}
				}
				
			}
		}
	}

	@media (width > 768px) {
		.about {
			background-size: 10rem, cover;
			background-position:top 3rem right;
			.about__article {
				.about__flex {
					display: flex;
					align-items: center;
					flex-direction: row-reverse;
					justify-content: center;
					gap: 2rem;
					background-color:var(--light-black);
					padding-left: 4rem;
				}
				.about__img__cont {
					max-width: 450px;
					align-self: stretch;
					margin-bottom: 0;
					max-height: unset;
					border-radius: unset;
				}
				.about__img {
					border-radius: 0 1rem 1rem 0;
				}
				.about__text {
					text-align: left;
					max-width: 54ch;
					padding: 2rem 0;
				}
				.about__title {
					margin-bottom: 4rem;
				}
			}
			.features__article {
				margin-top: 5rem;
				.features__list {
					grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
					max-width: 100%;
					.features__item {
						transition: transform 0.3s ease;
						cursor: pointer;
						&:hover {
							transform: scale(1.05);
							background-color: var(--primary-hover);
						}
					}
				}
				.features__title {
					margin-bottom: 4rem;
				}
			}
				.about__footer {
					flex-direction: row;
					margin-top: 2rem;
					.about__ending {
						max-width: 50ch;
						text-align: left;
					}
					.about__btn {
						margin: unset;
						transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
						&:hover {
							background-color: var(--primary-hover);
						}
					}
				}
			}
			
		}
	@media (width > 1200px) {
		.about {
			background-size: 18rem, cover;
		}
	}
</style>